  "prompt": "What is the meaning of Quora?",
  "response": "Quora is a question-and-answer platform where users can ask questions and receive answers from the community. The name \"Quora\" is derived from the term \"quorum,\" which refers to the minimum number of members required to make the proceedings of a meeting valid. This reflects the idea that a diverse group of people can come together to share knowledge and insights on various topics. Users can also contribute their expertise by answering questions, and the platform covers a wide range of subjects, from technology and science to personal experiences and hobbies. The goal of Quora is to provide a space for information exchange and learning.",
